commitResults.messageTitle: Create Mike chatbot with Echo and Bye commands
commitResults.messageBody:
*Add Main driver class
*Add inputHandler class to parse user input
*Add Command interface for future commands
*Add Echo command class that echos user input
*Add Bye command class that exits the chatbot

*InputHandler was added following SRP
*Command interface was added due to support expected future command

commitResults.messageTitle: Add TaskList, List, and Add commands
commitResults.messageBody:
* Add Task interface for future task types
* Add TaskList as a data structure for storing Tasks
* Add List command that prints list of tasks
* Add functionality of implicit adding tasks to list when no command is specified
* Modified existing InputHandler to accept new commands
* Modified Command interface to support taskList

*Task interface was added to support expected future task types

commitResults.messageTitle: Add Done command and related exception handling
commitResults.messageBody:
* Add TaskList as a data structure for storing Tasks
* Add Done command that marks a task as done and return the modified TaskList
* Modified Task to abstract class to support default Task class behaviours
* Removed Section of commented code in Mike class

ExceptionCommand class was added as a way of communicating that an exception has been thrown to the Mike chatbot.

commitResults.messageTitle: Add TodoCommand as child of AddCommand
commitResults.messageBody:
* Add TodoCommand that inherits default behaviour from Addcommand
* Modified AddCommand to an abstract class due to default behaviours for Tasks
* Add Task type identifiers in Task toStrings()

commitResults.messageTitle: Add Event functionality with requisite basic input exception handling
commitResults.messageBody:
* Add EventCommand as a child of AddCommand
* Add exception handling for catching of inputs that do not match Event and Todo format

commitResults.messageTitle: Add regex for basic input exception handling in Event and Todo commands
commitResults.messageBody:
* Add regex input checking for todo and event commands
* Modified default behaviour for AddCommand abstract class

* Add DeadlineTask class as child of task to represent deadline tasks
* Add DeadlineCommand class as child of AddCommand to allow Mike chatbot
  to execute the adding of deadline tasks to the list
* Fixed missing taskType variable in EventTask

* Fix InputHandler class to accept multiple succesive commands.
----Previous revisions had scanner object declared within InputHandler
    instance resulting in buffered lines to be forgotten
----Declared scanner in Main and passed it as an argument to
    InputHandler
* Add text-ui-test for testing of basic command functionality

commitResults.messageTitle: Add custom exception class for incorrect inputs
Add exception handling for existing commands
commitResults.messageBody:
* Modify InputHandler to throw exceptions upon invalid inputs instead of
 returning ExceptionCommands

* Add OutputHandler to format all outputs
* Modify DeleteCommand execution to fit delete function
* Modify existing classes to output a response with no formatting
